{"tid":2207163,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN/PC] 差唔多成億人都識玩既GAME我地連登無人講？","createTime":"2020-09-18T03:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T03:59:46.000Z","uid":53813,"like":8,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4bd45d37fab5b57826cec1c46598160f69487d","tid":2207163,"uid":53813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrZ4dKE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrZ4dKE.png&h=1dfb46a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <strong>遊戲背景介紹</strong><br />\n《Among Us》最初是於 2018 年在行動裝置上推出，而 2020 年 8 月的下載量則是較上月成長 616%，來到 1,840 萬，在夏季證明了他們是一匹黑馬。<br />\n自 2020 年 9 月 1 日至 14 日，較上月的新安裝數則長 127%，且目前仍持續成長中。在 8 月到 9 月的 45 天之間，就已經佔了該作品 70% 的總下載量，後勢看漲。<br />\n《Among Us》透過 YouTube 及 Twitch 等實況及影片快速擴散後，引起了越來越多的關注，所以漸漸有更多的內容創作者投入了《Among Us》的影片及實況，引發話題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XnPLHDb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXnPLHDb.png&h=b490dc3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而 8、9 月下載量提升最高的國家包含了美國、墨西哥、韓國以及菲律賓，其餘地區的安裝量也有所增加。<br />\n <br />\n<strong>下載Among US / 太空狼人殺 方法</strong><br />\nApple IOS:<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/among-us/id1351168404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Famong-us%2Fid1351168404&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=e715cfc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/among-us/id1351168404</a><br />\nGoogle Play: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.innersloth.spacemafia&amp;hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.innersloth.spacemafia%26hl%3Den&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=6ded6f1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.innersloth.spacemafia&amp;hl=en</a><br />\n中文版的Steam: <a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/945360/Among_Us/?l=tchinese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F945360%2FAmong_Us%2F%3Fl%3Dtchinese&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=cc05b19c\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/945360/Among_Us/?l=tchinese</a><br />\n <br />\n宜家YOUTUBE 隨便一條片都過百萬人睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地連登仔呢? 無人講? 是唔是無人識玩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地連登仔點可以唔識？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻睇左呢條教學片，即刻去玩，我地連登遊戲台又點會簡單既GAME都唔識？係咪？係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎緊聖誕節如果個個人都識玩但你唔識玩你唔好講自己有上連登遊戲台<br />\n<br />\n全世界都有人玩，香港YOUTUBER打機當然都有人玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50rRDcx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50rRDcx.png&h=65869020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>教學</strong><br />\n我終於搵到人有肯出教學片，仲要識廣東話既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W9q_L-Zd5IM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW9q_L-Zd5IM&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=1086f7ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W9q_L-Zd5IM</a><br />\n<br />\n外國人的Discord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/tpFsQbU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FtpFsQbU&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=a8e25342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/tpFsQbU</a><br />\n台灣人的Discord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/WeFHKzk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FWeFHKzk&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=5bdc079a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/WeFHKzk</a><br />\n香港人的Discord:<ins><span class=\"red\">唔好意思，有待跟進</span></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"